  "extract": "Robert Sanford Havoc Pennington is an American computer engineer and entrepreneur. He is known in the free software movement due to his work on HAL, GNOME, Metacity, GConf, and D-Bus.",
  "extract_html": "<p><b>Robert Sanford Havoc Pennington</b> is an American computer engineer and entrepreneur. He is known in the free software movement due to his work on HAL, GNOME, Metacity, GConf, and D-Bus.</p>"
